{"word":"Jaazaniah","slug":"jaazaniah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jaazaniah</b> 1. Called Jezaniah, a captain who joined Gedaliah at Mizpah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=23'>2Ki 25:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=8'>Jer 40:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=42&verse=1'>Jer 42:1</a><br/> 2. A Rechabite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=35&verse=3'>Jer 35:3</a><br/> 3. An idolatrous zealot<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=11'>Eze 8:11</a><br/> 4. A wicked prince of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=11&verse=13'>Eze 11:13</a>"}]}